<br>
Wizard Disciplines<br>
<br>
RESISTANT (Level 30): +3 to all resistances increasing to +10 at 50th level. This discipline lasts for 1 minute, and has a base reuse time of 1 hour. The reuse time for this discipline will decrease as you level.<br>
<br>
FEARLESS (Level 40): Immunity to &quot;Fear&quot; and all spells that cause &quot;fear&quot;. This discipline lasts for 30 seconds, and has a base reuse time of 1 hour. The reuse time for this discipline will decrease as you level.<br>
<br>
SPECIALIZATION (Level 52): The wizard will cast all spells as if they were all under his primary specialization skill. This discipline lasts for 3 minutes, and has a base reuse time of 15 minutes. The reuse time for this discipline will decrease as the wizard gains additional levels.<br>
<br>
RESEARCH MASTERY (Level 53): The wizard will be able to research spells as if he had a skill of 255. This discipline lasts for 3 minutes, and has a base reuse time of 15 minutes. The reuse time for this discipline will decrease as the wizard gains additional levels.<br>
<br>
CONCENTRATION (Level 54): The wizard will be able to cast spells without requiring the spell component(s). This discipline lasts for 1 minute, and has a base reuse time of 45 minutes. The reuse time for this discipline will decrease as the wizard gains additional levels.<br>
<br>
CHANNEL (Level 55): When using this discipline, the wizard will be able to cast spells without being interrupted. This discipline lasts for 10 seconds, and has a base reuse time of 60 minutes. The reuse time for this discipline will decrease as the wizard gains additional levels.<br>
<br>
<br>
